name: Fitness Mobile App UI Kit
description: This kit is carefully crafted and contains many UI components that you can use for design inspiration or speed up your design workflow. You can also find a series of screens that guide users through the app interface & functions. You can make your custom workout on this app. You can track your daily activity & set up an alarm for your exercise time. Easy to customize to fit your style. Also, You can get a dark mode version of it. Available in Figma, XD & Sketch
